@startuml DeleteClass
|Admin|
start
:1. Open class list;
:2. Select class to delete;
:3. Confirm deletion;
|ClassManagementUI|
:4. Send delete request;
|ClassController|
:5. Verify class exists;
:6. Check for enrolled students;
:7. Delete class from backend;
|Database|
:8. Remove class record;
|ClassController|
:9. Return success;
|ClassManagementUI|
:10. Display confirmation;
:11. Refresh class list;
stop
@enduml
